   <summary> Nothing casts a chill in the heart of a fancy-free Web surfer than all this talk lately of Hulu incorporating some type of a subscription model. Yes, you heard me right. That free site of the latest (and even...</summary> 
   <author> 
      <name>Gus Sentementes</name> 
      
   </author> 
         <category term="*NEWS*" scheme="http://www.sixapart.com/ns/types#category" /> 
